job.title: ASRB Recruitment 2021  Apply Online for NET, ARS & STO Vacancy
job.body:
Total Vacancies:287

Name of the post:

  • Agricultural Research Service (ARS) & Senior Technical Officer (STO)

Description:

The Agricultural Scientists Recruitment Board (ASRB) issued a total of 287 vacancies for the posts of Agricultural Research Service (ARS) & Senior Technical Officer (STO). The online application for these posts under ASRB shall start from 05-04-2021 at 10:00 AM. The eligible and interested candidates can apply for this online application before 10-05-2021 till 05:00 PM. For further detailed information regarding educational qualifications, age limit, selection procedure, how to apply, etc. for these posts is mentioned below. For more such updates do visit theprograd.com .The ProGrad jobs.

 

Mode of application & application fee:

The application fee for ASRB Recruitment 2021 :

Mode of application: Online

For more details, you can refer to the notification. The link is given at the bottom.

Important dates:

  • The Starting date to apply online is 05-04-2021 at 10:00 AM
  • The Last date to apply online is 10-05-2021 till 05:00 PM
  • Last date and time for making online fee payment: 25-04-2021 till 05:00 PM
  • Date for Combined Preliminary Exam: During 21-06-2021 to 27-06-2021
  • Date for ARS-2021 (Mains) Examination: 19-09-2021
  • Date of Interview for the post of STO (T-6): To be notified later 
  • Date of Viva-voce for ARS-2021 Examination: To be notified later 

Educational qualification:

You must have the Masters in the relevant field to apply for the post of Agricultural Research Service (ARS) & Senior Technical Officer (STO)

Age limit criteria:

For NET: 

  • Minimum Age: 21 years
  • There is no upper age limit for the NET.

For ARS: 

  • Minimum Age: 21 Years
  • Maximum Age: 32 Years

For STO (as of 25-04-2021)

  • Minimum Age: 21 Years
  • Maximum Age: not have attained the 35 Years

For age relaxation criteria, you can refer to the notification. The link is given below in The ProGrad jobs.


Pay Scale:

  • The pay scale as per 7th pay commission for the post of Agricultural Research Service (ARS) & Senior Technical Officer (STO) is as per norms
  • Check the detailed notification also something has missed.

Detailed vacancies:

The vacancies in detail are given below. Check below that ASRB issued this notification for which posts.

 

How to apply for ASRB Recruitment 2021?

  • First, visit the official website.
  • Register yourself on the portal of ASRB.
  • Login yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification of the Agricultural Research Service (ARS) & Senior Technical Officer (STO).
  • Fill up the complete details that are asked in the application form.
  • Upload your photo and signature with the dimensions asked in the instructions.
  • Submit the application fee
  • Finally, download the application form for future needs.

How to prepare for the ASRB exam?

Try this strategy to crack any exam:

  • You must have the syllabus.
  • Give a brief reading of the syllabus.
  • Buy a previous year's papers book.
  • See the most frequent topics that came in previous papers.
  • First, finish them and revise them on daily basis.
  • Recommended books to crack this exam.
  • The final and most important steps are to revise, revise and revise.
